          <p>
            Fund Investigator provides analytical tools and information about mutual funds. The service is provided for informational purposes only and does not constitute financial advice.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mt-12 mb-6">3. Data and Information</h2>
          <p>
            All fund data is sourced from AMFI (Association of Mutual Funds in India). While we strive for accuracy, we make no warranties about the completeness, reliability, or accuracy of this information.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-4">
